## Specs-D2 RelationsPanel & AutoLinkContent
**Status:** draft

**状态：** 已实现
**模块：** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/components/`
**标签：** stack:frontend
**依赖于：** UiSystem-A1

```typescript
// RelationsPanel.vue
interface RelationsPanelProps {
  item: SpecItem
}

// AutoLinkContent.vue
interface AutoLinkContentProps {
  content: string
}
// Regex: /\b([GRAPTVXIS]\d+(?:\.\d+)?)\b/
```

| 字段 | 类型 | 描述 |
|---|---|---|
| `parents` | `{ id, title, section_type, status }[]` | 上游 depends_on |
| `children` | `{ id, title, section_type, status }[]` | 下游关联 |

```
fn render(content):
    parts = splitByRegex(content, ID_REF_REGEX)
    for part in parts:
        if part.matches(ID_REF_REGEX):
            render(<SpecLink id={part} />)
        else:
            render(<span>{part}</span>)
```


