## Specs-D3 GateBanner（规范视图）
**Status:** draft

**状态：** 已实现
**模块：** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/components/GateBanner.vue`
**标签：** stack:frontend
**依赖于：** UiSystem-A1, Relay-D6

```typescript
interface GateBannerProps {
  sectionId: string
  gate: PendingGate
}

// Events
emit('approve', gateId: string)
emit('reject', gateId: string)
emit('openInChat', gateId: string)
```

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Hidden: no active gate for section
    Hidden --> Visible: gate_reached for this section
    Visible --> Hidden: gate_resolved or approved
    Visible --> Expanded: user clicks View Diff
    Expanded --> Visible: user collapses diff
```

| 字段 | 类型 | 描述 |
|---|---|---|
| `sectionId` | `string` | 此横幅守卫的规范章节 |
| `gate.profession` | `string` | 等待者身份（例如 "architect"） |
| `gate.title` | `string` | 待审批内容的一行摘要 |
| `gate.since` | `number` | 关卡触发时间戳 |


